data.text: 1915-16 The League and FA Cup were not played between 1915 and 1919 because of the First World War. However, regional competitions and friendlies were played, with the squad made up of players who didn't go to war. 1939-40 The League and FA Cup were not played between 1939 and 1945 because of the Second World War. However, regional competitions and friendlies were played, with the squad made up of players who didn't go to war. The Football League War Cup was played during this era as a substitute for the FA Cup.
